## Architecture (SRP)

Package root: `unit_converter/` (lecture SSOT)

- `unit_converter/app/input_parser.py` ‚Äî parse & validate only
- `unit_converter/domain/unit_registry.py` ‚Äî register & lookup units (OCP)
- `unit_converter/domain/converter.py` ‚Äî meter-based conversion only
- `unit_converter/app/output_formatter.py` ‚Äî json | csv | table output only
- `unit_converter/infrastructure/config_loader.py` ‚Äî JSON/YAML load only
- `unit_converter/cli.py` ‚Äî orchestration only
- `unit_converter/__main__.py` ‚Äî `python -m unit_converter` entry
- `tests/test_converter.py` ¬∑ `tests/test_cli.py` ‚Äî **project root** (not under package; Dual-Track)

## Conversion constants (meter = 1.0)

- feet: 3.28084
- yard: 1.09361
- Display: round to 4 decimal places

## Error messages (exact strings)

- E-FMT: `Invalid format. Use unit:value (ex: meter:2.5)`
- E-NUM: `Invalid number: {value_str}`
- E-NEG: `Negative value not allowed`
- E-UNIT: `Unknown unit: {unit}`

